\subsection{Cloud test environment simulation}
It turns out that the robustness, safety and reliability of a smart grid can be tested upfront in various manners. There is the safety and performance requirement on one hand towards the software of a single device in the grid and on the other hand towards the interplay of many component - in the end the entire smart grid. 

